### Decision Engine API Tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### Get LLM Config
GET http://localhost:8080/config_llm

###

### Test 1: Greeting
POST http://localhost:8080/decide
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Привет",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "chat_id": 12345
}

###

### Test 2: Request operator
POST http://localhost:8080/decide
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Хочу поговорить с оператором",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "chat_id": 12345
}

