### Test 12: Long conversation history test
# First message
POST http://localhost:8080/decide
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Привет",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "chat_id": 55555
}

###

# Follow-up message (same chat_id to build history)
POST http://localhost:8080/decide
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "У меня вопрос по услугам",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "chat_id": 55555
}

###

# Continue conversation
POST http://localhost:8080/decide
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Какие услуги вы предоставляете?",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "chat_id": 55555
}

###
